ふいに点滅し始め 急かすのかな
Does it suddenly start flashing to hurry me up?

363
00:40:00,064 --> 00:40:01,064
ふいに点滅し始め 急かすのかな
Suddenly starting to blink, is it rushing me?

364
00:40:01,184 --> 00:40:08,414
いつの間にか少し 早歩きになってた
Without realizing it, I've started walking a bit faster.

365
00:40:08,964 --> 00:40:15,164
自分の意思 関係ないように
As if my own will has nothing to do with it.

366
00:40:15,564 --> 00:40:22,064
誰も彼もみんな 一斉に走り出す
Everyone, one and all, starts running at once.

367
00:40:22,664 --> 00:40:29,264
何に追われ焦るのかと笑う
I laugh, wondering what they're being chased by to be in such a hurry.

368
00:40:29,764 --> 00:40:39,564
客観的に見てる私が 嫌いだ
I hate myself for watching so objectively.

369
00:40:40,064 --> 00:40:46,564
決心のきっかけは 理屈ではなくて
The motivation for a decision isn't logic.

370
00:40:46,964 --> 00:40:53,064
いつだってこの胸の衝動から始まる
It always starts from an impulse in my chest.

371
00:40:54,064 --> 00:41:00,064
流されてしまうこと 抵抗しながら
While resisting being swept away...

372
00:41:00,864 --> 00:41:08,864
生きるとは選択肢 たった一つを選ぶこと
To live is to choose just one option.

373
00:41:09,564 --> 00:41:16,864
横断歩道 渡っていつも思う
I always think while crossing the crosswalk.

374
00:41:17,464 --> 00:41:23,964
こんな風に心に信号があればいい
I wish there were traffic lights in the heart like this.

375
00:41:24,364 --> 00:41:30,064
進みなさい それから 止まりなさい
"Go ahead," and then, "Stop."

376
00:41:30,464 --> 00:41:37,564
それがルールならば 悩まずに行けるけれど…
If those were the rules, I could go without worrying, but...

377
00:41:38,264 --> 00:41:44,864
誰かの指示 待ち続けたくない
I don't want to keep waiting for someone's instructions.

378
00:41:45,364 --> 00:41:51,364
走りたい時に 自分で踏み出せる
To be able to step out on my own when I want to run.

379
00:41:51,964 --> 00:41:58,564
強い意志を持った人でいたい
I want to be a person with a strong will.

380
00:41:59,064 --> 00:42:08,864
もう一人の明日の私を 探そう
Let's find the another me of tomorrow.

381
00:42:09,364 --> 00:42:15,964
決心のきっかけは 時間切れじゃなくて
The motivation for a decision isn't running out of time.

382
00:42:16,364 --> 00:42:22,764
考えたその上で未来を信じること
It's about believing in the future after thinking it through.

383
00:42:23,264 --> 00:42:29,864
後悔はしたくない 思ったそのまま
I don't want to have regrets, just as I thought.

384
00:42:30,264 --> 00:42:39,564
正解はわからない たった一度の人生だ
I don't know the right answer, it's my only life.

385
00:42:40,064 --> 00:42:46,064
