As if lured, everyone starts running.

387
00:42:53,464 --> 00:43:00,564
自分のこと 自分で決められず
Unable to decide my own matters for myself,

388
00:43:00,964 --> 00:43:07,564
背中を押すもの 欲しいんだ
I want something to push me forward.

389
00:43:07,864 --> 00:43:11,864
きっかけ
Motivation.

390
00:43:12,464 --> 00:43:18,864
決心のきっかけは 理屈ではなくて
The motivation for a decision isn't logic.

391
00:43:19,364 --> 00:43:25,764
いつだってこの胸の衝動から始まる
It always starts from an impulse in my chest.

392
00:43:26,564 --> 00:43:32,864
流されてしまうこと 抵抗しながら
While resisting being swept away...

393
00:43:33,264 --> 00:43:40,064
生きるとは選択肢 たった一つを選ぶこと
To live is to choose just one option.

394
00:43:40,464 --> 00:43:47,564
決心は自分から 思ったそのまま…
The decision comes from within, just as I thought...

395
00:43:48,464 --> 00:43:52,064
生きよう
Let's live.

