But don't force a smile, either.

436
00:47:41,072 --> 00:47:44,572
ゆっくり空見上げてよう
Let's slowly look up at the sky.

437
00:47:44,572 --> 00:47:48,072
似た者同士で
Since we're two of a kind.

438
00:47:48,072 --> 00:47:56,072
翼を傷めた君　今度は私が支えるから
You with the hurt wings, this time I'll support you.

439
00:47:56,572 --> 00:48:02,572
消えかけた夢に涙した日もあったけれど
There were days I cried over fading dreams.

440
00:48:02,572 --> 00:48:09,572
君の言う“大丈夫”で諦めずに来れた
But thanks to your "It's okay," I could keep going.

441
00:48:09,572 --> 00:48:16,572
まだ遅くないよ　ここから始まるストーリー
It's not too late. The story begins here.

442
00:48:16,572 --> 00:48:20,572
さあ少し休んで
Now, take a little rest.

443
00:48:20,572 --> 00:48:27,072
涙を拭いて歩きだそう
Wipe your tears and let's start walking.

444
00:48:28,072 --> 00:48:34,072
覚えてる？私もね　折れかけた翼抱いて
Remember? I was also holding onto broken wings.

445
00:48:34,072 --> 00:48:38,072
励ます君に甘えてた
Relying on you while you cheered me on.

446
00:48:38,072 --> 00:48:41,072
ほらあの日のこと
Look back at that day.

447
00:48:41,072 --> 00:48:48,072
雨上がりの刹那に　私たちは強く生まれ変わる
In the moment after the rain, we're reborn strong.

448
00:48:49,572 --> 00:48:56,072
心無い声に耳をふさぐ日もあるけれど
Some days we shut out heartless voices.

449
00:48:56,072 --> 00:49:00,072
味方がここにいる
But an ally is right here.

450
00:49:00,072 --> 00:49:03,572
手当ては任せてよ
Leave the healing to me.

451
00:49:03,572 --> 00:49:10,072
また増えてゆくよ　これから叶えるストーリー
They'll keep growing, the stories we'll fulfill.

452
00:49:10,072 --> 00:49:14,072
さあ手を取り合って
Now, let's take each other's hands.

453
00:49:14,072 --> 00:49:20,072
遥か彼方を見つめよう
And look toward the far horizon.

454
00:49:20,072 --> 00:49:26,572
これから先は傷つかずには進めない
From now on, we can't move forward without getting hurt.

455
00:49:26,572 --> 00:49:29,572
だけど覚えてて
But please remember...

456
00:49:29,572 --> 00:49:38,072
君はもう一人じゃないから胸を張って
...you're not alone anymore, so hold your head high.

457
00:49:39,072 --> 00:49:45,572
私たち今も不器用で無邪気な小鳥
We're still clumsy and innocent little birds.

458
00:49:45,572 --> 00:49:50,072
譲れない夢抱いて
Holding onto dreams we won't give up.

459
00:49:50,072 --> 00:49:54,072
翼はためかせよう　大空へ…
Let's flap our wings to the wide sky...

